The paper discusses a new optimizer for training deep learning models, specifically focusing on adaptive regularization. This topic falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). Additionally, the paper includes experiments on deep learning benchmarks (cs.CV) and discusses the optimization of non-convex functions (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves matrix computations, which is a common topic in data science (cs.DS).
